[training:blogPost] > jnt:content, mix:title, jmix:editorialContent, trainingmix:component, jmix:mainResource
 - subtitle (string, textarea) i18n mandatory
 - cover (weakreference) mandatory < jmix:image
 - body (string, richtext) i18n mandatory
 - authors (weakreference, choicelist[nodes='$currentSite/contents/blog/authors;training:teamMember']) multiple < training:teamMember
 - blogDate (date)
